descriptionHtml: The plan is for this mod to be a technical showcase--each part another interesting thing implemented or annoyance smoothed away.  Play with it, learn from it, or even use my small contributions for your bigger and better mod.  With every new release, I will include a detailed account of how to do it yourself.
author: Sparafucile

files.name: Automation
files.changelogHtml: Breezehome alchemy workbench scripted to move ingredients between the satchel on top of it and player inventory.
